LEDSINO,is a professional led display supplier, an innovative team who’s devoted to improving led display technology around the world.

And also an industry leader in led wall display developing, manufacturing, and online distributing.Serving customers in both domestic and abroad market.

Our main focus has always been designing and manufacturing electronic outdoor/indoor led display, rental led display, flexible led display, led sphere display and transparent window display.

Since established in 2011, our team has been innovating new ways to deliver the highest quality products, services and value to our customers.Our led screens’ projects include some of the most advanced technology and forward-thinking design in the market today.
